{
  "stem": "17761.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 95.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we sailed, and the destroyer became a-- our company.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then there were two destroyers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then there were more destroyers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We ended up with eight destroyers and two little ships.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So we had a [INAUDIBLE] of our own--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in that transport.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we reached the-- the-- we got near to Eretz Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were about 40 miles from Israel, still not in the Israeli-- the-- the British-- at that time, it was British Mandate-- territory-- territorial waters.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Two destroyers attacked us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just closed our way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And oh, they didn't know one thing-- that our ship was a icebreaker.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he, the-- the-- the captain of the ship went into one of the destroyers to make a huge hole.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They to-- to-- to tow away this destroyer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they immediately started to throw [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] tear bombs, tear gas-- bombs with tear gas.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And naturally we all had tears in our eyes and there's burns everywhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the only thing that we did, we could do, was we all sang the 'Hatikvah'-- once, twice, three times, four times, for endless.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And suddenly, there was dark, because the Haganah people, they-- they destroyed the engine, everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no electricity, no ventilation, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we continued to inhale this tear gas and to sing the 'Hatikvah.' And naturally, they came on the boat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they towed us away with another destroyer into Haifa.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was again-- I don't know how it came-- there was a [NON-ENGLISH]-- same day as we were deported from home to Transnistria, the same day we were deported from Haifa to Cyprus.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The evening of Hoshana Rabbah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'Barb-led?'",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Barbed wires.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so they brought us to Famagusta, which is a port in Cyprus.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
